
'''* Book: Legal Frameworks on Social and Solidarity Economy: What is the Role of Civil Society Organizations in Policy Making?''' Think pieces for the UNRISD conference “Potential and Limits of Social and Solidarity Economy”. 6-8 May 2013. By Rafael Peels, May 2013

